{"tid":1740631,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【恥笑，TVB台慶只剩零星廣告】繼續每日洗版任務 - 高科技神仙水 \"AQ\"","createTime":"2019-11-20T04:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T01:40:45.000Z","uid":267969,"like":64,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"6ef8aed858c91a86832766c82033b9600e3ec651","tid":1740631,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T04:06:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">速報！</span></span></strong><br />\n尋日我哋TVB抵制team 搞《全民洗版「賀」台慶》真係一路睇一路笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣告一係hardcore藍絲、一係就<span style=\"color: red;\">老人驅風品牌</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n節目裡面，連送獎品按摩椅等等，都<span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢開贊助商名</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍵盤戰士洗洗下版，<span style=\"color: red;\">某啲FB都要關page</span>，唔通想重演online版831事件，清post清留言block網民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/50aLiFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F50aLiFE.jpg&h=f31041df&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLaLiFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLaLiFE.jpg&h=c473c7a7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後，喺度再次多謝有份參戰嘅連登仔，冇你哋推post洗版，唔會咁成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想回帶補做台慶任務嘅，請用追故模式到：</strong><br />\n號召連登大軍打殘TVB，全民洗版&quot;賀&quot;台慶！ - <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737598</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">好喇，回歸每日任務～<br />\n抗爭要堅持，柒TVB要成每日習慣<br />\n只需每日幾秒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【抵制CCTVB 每日任務】</span></strong><br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.<span style=\"color: red;\">推post</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n4.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n5. tag 多幾個friend做任 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真，P牌每日只開一個抵制TVB行動post<br />\n唔會開9up post，<span style=\"color: red;\">請follow我個acc</span>、推post<br />\n<br />\n是日精選@20 Nov 2019 <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>AQ水</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AQbiosanitizer/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAQbiosanitizer%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=ececdd66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AQbiosanitizer/</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>※記得用留言template</strong></span></span><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留言重點</span></strong>係全力阻止廣告商簽訂下年合約</strong> <br />\n<blockquote>無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/74344681_500165227506998_3839387131227144192_o.png?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_oc=AQmZAx9XoOqYHQftS1g6HLaFXBFZ-x-wz60xqR9DvUXfU74Lq4Ui-z-Fh2HAs8_K9ug&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=dfaafa584b000609941e1c8d413fde45&amp;oe=5E817B41\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F74344681_500165227506998_3839387131227144192_o.png%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_oc%3DAQmZAx9XoOqYHQftS1g6HLaFXBFZ-x-wz60xqR9DvUXfU74Lq4Ui-z-Fh2HAs8_K9ug%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Ddfaafa584b000609941e1c8d413fde45%26oe%3D5E817B41&h=6dcbbb6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎用呢幅圖留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&h=ffeb70a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OFB5XW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OFB5XW.jpg&h=34f0d91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>講下臭屎</strong></span><br />\n「AQ是高科技產品，也是高能量產品，不但淨化環境，也淨化負能量分子，有利健康和運氣」<br />\n符水呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n賣到1000蚊1L，原諒我笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: TVB廣告客戶名單！！</strong></span> <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=83c361c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a>  <br />\n －－－－－－－ <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請即follow:</span></strong> <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb%2F&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=f01a040b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb/</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb <br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=qnfk3FWFLoR313jZLhvcNuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=b462e24f\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 抵制綜合組: <a hre